#postcorona #quarantine 
Post corona. We should be used to be under the quarantine and have distance. I came back to Korea 5th July and had 2 weeks Quarantine and had injured a bit and then had another quarantine in the hospital after a short freedom. If I want to go out somewhere again for the training then should had another quarantine there and here coming back again. 

I should be professional for many many 2 weeks meditations, some dry trainings and times being alone. 

I could hear the sounds from the nature and the air, see the tiny things been surrounded us, feel the things we missed usaully. Be awake. Be there. Realize the moment.
